, and then there is the quality of the food, with raw meat being served to athletes.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"certain foods\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"eggs\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"chicken\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"certain carbohydrates\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"raw meat\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have got to improve it over the next couple of days dramatically.\\\"\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next couple\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Anson also explained how the discontent had forced team bosses to take action, with some stars even making their own packed lunches.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"score\": 0.9999999479514385, \"rank\": 5.203779642786111e-08, \"text\": \"Anson\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the discontent\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"team bosses\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"some stars\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"their own packed lunches\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our athletes have decided they would rather go and eat in our performance lodge in Clichy, so we are having to get another chef to come over as the demand is far exceeding what we thought it would be,\\\" he said.\", \"from\"